// use ternary representation approach, jaise hi 2 aa jaaaye to return false, jaise hm binary nikalte hai, same aise hi ternary bhi nikalni hai, last mein return true
// TC = O of log base 3 n = O(log3n)

class Solution {
    public boolean checkPowersOfThree(int n) {
        while(n>0){
            if(n%3 == 2){
                return false;
            }
            n=n/3;
        }
        return true;
    }
}
